      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our heart’s desire is not the peace so sweet,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our longed for hope is not the joy we’ll meet;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But Thou Thyself, Thou art “our hope,” O Lord,"
